<Link id="l00010" /><CodeLine lineNumber="10"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - instrument each function with a call to &#95;&#95;CheckForDebuggerJustMyCode. The</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00011" /><CodeLine lineNumber="11"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   sole argument should be defined in .msvcjmc. Each flag is 1 byte initilized</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00013" /><CodeLine lineNumber="13"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - create the dummy COMDAT function &#95;&#95;JustMyCode&#95;Default to prevent linking</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00014" /><CodeLine lineNumber="14"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   error if &#95;&#95;CheckForDebuggerJustMyCode is not available.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00015" /><CodeLine lineNumber="15"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// - For MSVC:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00016" /><CodeLine lineNumber="16"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   add &quot;/alternatename:&#95;&#95;CheckForDebuggerJustMyCode=&#95;&#95;JustMyCode&#95;Default&quot; to</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00017" /><CodeLine lineNumber="17"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   &quot;llvm.linker.options&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00018" /><CodeLine lineNumber="18"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   For ELF:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00019" /><CodeLine lineNumber="19"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   Rename &#95;&#95;JustMyCode&#95;Default to &#95;&#95;CheckForDebuggerJustMyCode and mark it as</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00020" /><CodeLine lineNumber="20"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   weak symbol.</span></CodeLine>
